  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Edema</measure>
    <time_frame>after 6 days of diclofenac and placebo</time_frame>
    <description>Presence of edema, measured by the estimative of total body water (deuterium oxide dilution technique). The measurements will be done in the end of 6 days of use of placebo and diclofenac, and the delta between diclofenac and placebo will be used as endpoint</description>
  </primary_outcome>
